snippet.title: L'Oreal  Infallible 24H Fresh Wear Foundation || 300 Amber ||Demo & Review || Divya Kataria
snippet.description:
Hey Guys!
In this video i am going to review the loreal 24 hr freshwear foundation..
I got the shade amber 300 which is the second last shade😑
in this video we did oxidation test, demo with and without color corrector...
Watch full video to know  about my opinion on it..
